 disk nitrogen is efficiently converted from NH$_3$ to N$_2$,\nsignificantly increasing the volatility of nitrogen in planet-forming regions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 10 Feb 2019 18:16:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-03"}
