uggest that low barrier circular IMA magnets may be more\nsuitable for this application.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 10 Feb 2019 18:37:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 20 Apr 2019 19:13:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-23"}
