egral open book decompositions, the\nhat version of ECK is supported in Alexander gradings less than or equal to\ntwice the genus of the knot.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Feb 2019 00:08:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-12"}
