 Then, we prove the security of the proposed OABS\nand the protocol as well. Finally, we implement smart contract in Solidity to\ndemonstrate the validity of the proposed protocol.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Feb 2019 03:34:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-12"}
