e stars: EPs from flares are contained\nby the stellar magnetic field; and potential CMEs that might generate EPs at\nlarger distances also fail to escape.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Feb 2019 05:04:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-27"}
